# JEI Info — Glitch-Infused Ingot
deepmoblearning.glitch_ingot.jei_info_1=TLDR: Drop some fragments, terrestrial artifacts and stellar alloy ingots into a body of water and hope for the best
deepmoblearning.glitch_ingot.jei_info_2=You've found that terrestrial artifacts are a good stabilization agent for Unstable glitch fragments.
deepmoblearning.glitch_ingot.jei_info_3=After the fragments are stable, they desperately seek out a material to latch on to, you think that stellar alloy might be strong enough as a host.
deepmoblearning.glitch_ingot.jei_info_4=The entire process is delicate, it needs to be performed in water or the materials wont bind properly.
